flowchart TD
    A[Create Device Request] --> B[Validate JWT Token]
    B --> C{Token Valid?}
    C -->|No| D[Return 401 Unauthorized]
    C -->|Yes| E[Check Admin Permissions]
    E --> F{Admin Access?}
    F -->|No| G[Return 403 Forbidden]
    F -->|Yes| H[Validate Device Data]
    H --> I{Valid Device Info?}
    I -->|No| J[Return 400 Invalid Data]
    I -->|Yes| K[Check Device Serial Uniqueness]
    K --> L{Serial Number Available?}
    L -->|No| M[Return 409 Serial Already Exists]
    L -->|Yes| N[Generate Device ID]
    N --> O[Generate Registration Code]
    O --> P[Insert Device Record]
    P --> Q[Set Device Status to Pending]
    Q --> R[Cache Device Data]
    R --> S[Log Device Creation]
    S --> T[Return 201 Device Created]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style D fill:#ffebee
    style G fill:#ffebee
    style J fill:#ffebee
    style M fill:#ffebee
    style T fill:#e8f5e8